docs.lead_paragraph: The Collins steamship Atlantic, Captain WEST, arrived at her wharf at 8 o'clock on Saturday evening. She left Liverpool at 12 1/4 o'clock on Wednesday afternoon, the 26th ult. The Europa arrived at Liverpool at midning of Sunday the 23d. On entering the Mersey she run down a small schooner, but there was no loss of life.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Chair of the House of Representatives has not for many years been filled by a gentleman of more dignified and imposing personal appearance that its present popular occupant, Colonel LIAN BOYD. He must be between fifty and sixty years of age, but old father Time has dealt gently by him.
